'''2020年7月亞美尼亞－阿塞拜疆武裝衝突'''，或慣常被亞美尼亞人称为'''塔沃什冲突''' ({{Lang-hy|Տավուշի բախումները}}）（{{IPA-hy|tɑvuʃiˈ bɑχumnɛˈɹə}})，被亞塞拜彊人稱為'''塔烏茲冲突''' ({{Lang-az|Tovuz döyüşləri}})，或'''七月冲突''' ({{Lang-hy|Հուլիսյան բախումներ}} {{IPA-hy|hulisjɑˈn bɑχumnɛˈɹ}}, {{Lang-az|İyul döyüşləri}})，是[[亚美尼亚武装力量|亚美尼亚武装力量]]和阿塞拜疆武裝力量間始於2020年7月12日的武裝衝突事件。最初的衝突發生在亞美尼亞[[塔武什省|塔武什省]]的Movses附近<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.civilnet.am/news/2020/07/13/%D5%84%D5%B8%D5%BE%D5%BD%D5%A5%D5%BD-%D5%A3%D5%B5%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%B2%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%B4-%D5%A1%D5%A4%D6%80%D5%A2%D5%A5%D5%BB%D5%A1%D5%B6%D5%A1%D5%AF%D5%A1%D5%B6-%D5%AF%D5%B8%D5%B2%D5%B4%D5%AB%D6%81-%D5%AF%D6%80%D5%A1%D5%AF%D5%B8%D6%81%D5%B6%D5%A5%D6%80%D5%B6-%D5%A1%D6%80%D5%B1%D5%A1%D5%AF%D5%BE%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%B4-%D5%A5%D5%B6-%D5%A3%D5%B5%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%B2%D5%AB%D5%B6-%D5%B7%D5%A1%D5%BF-%D5%B4%D5%B8%D5%BF-%D5%B0%D5%A5%D5%BC%D5%A1%D5%BE%D5%B8%D6%80%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%A9%D5%B5%D5%A1%D5%B4%D5%A2%E2%80%A4-%D5%84%D4%BB%D5%8A/389695 |title=Մովսես գյուղում ադրբեջանական կողմից կրակոցներն արձակվում են գյուղին շատ մոտ հեռավորությամբ․ ՄԻՊ |date=12 July 2020 |accessdate=12 July 2020 |website=CivilNet |publisher=[[Civilitas_Foundation|Civilitas Foundation]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712225132/https://www.civilnet.am/news/2020/07/13/%D5%84%D5%B8%D5%BE%D5%BD%D5%A5%D5%BD-%D5%A3%D5%B5%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%B2%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%B4-%D5%A1%D5%A4%D6%80%D5%A2%D5%A5%D5%BB%D5%A1%D5%B6%D5%A1%D5%AF%D5%A1%D5%B6-%D5%AF%D5%B8%D5%B2%D5%B4%D5%AB%D6%81-%D5%AF%D6%80%D5%A1%D5%AF%D5%B8%D6%81%D5%B6%D5%A5%D6%80%D5%B6-%D5%A1%D6%80%D5%B1%D5%A1%D5%AF%D5%BE%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%B4-%D5%A5%D5%B6-%D5%A3%D5%B5%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%B2%D5%AB%D5%B6-%D5%B7%D5%A1%D5%BF-%D5%B4%D5%B8%D5%BF-%D5%B0%D5%A5%D5%BC%D5%A1%D5%BE%D5%B8%D6%80%D5%B8%D6%82%D5%A9%D5%B5%D5%A1%D5%B4%D5%A2%E2%80%A4-%D5%84%D4%BB%D5%8A/389695 |archive-date=2020-07-12 |language=hy |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及亞美尼亞－阿塞拜疆邊界的阿塞拜疆[[塔烏茲區|塔烏茲區]]的Ağdam<ref name="takhribat">{{Cite news |url=https://mod.gov.az/az/news/ermenistan-silahli-quvvelerinin-bolmeleri-tovuz-istiqametinde-texribat-toredib-31439.html |title=Ermənistan silahlı qüvvələrinin bölmələri Tovuz istiqamətində təxribat törədib |website=mod.gov.az |publisher=[[Ministry_of_Defence_(Azerbaijan)|Azerbaijan Ministry of Defence]] |date=12 July 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712131728/https://mod.gov.az/az/news/ermenistan-silahli-quvvelerinin-bolmeleri-tovuz-istiqametinde-texribat-toredib-31439.html |archive-date=2020-07-12 |accessdate=12 July 2020 |language=az |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

衝突於7月13日開始，一直持續到7月16日，造成至少16名軍事人員和1名平民傷亡。阿塞拜疆的軍事人員傷亡包括一名[[少將|少將]]、一名[[上校|上校]]和兩名[[少校|少校]]<ref name="mod">{{cite web |url=https://mod.gov.az/en/news/fierce-fighting-in-the-direction-of-tovuz-region-is-continuing-31471.html |title=Fierce fighting in the direction of Tovuz region is continuing |website=mod.gov.az |archive-date=2020-07-14 |publisher=Ministry of Defence of Azerbaijan |date=14 July 2020 |accessdate=14 July 2020 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714210744/https://mod.gov.az/en/news/fierce-fighting-in-the-direction-of-tovuz-region-is-continuing-31471.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亞美尼亞政府公告，在一場小規模衝突中，一名[[少校|少校]]、一名[[上尉|上尉]]和兩名[[中士|中士]]喪生<ref>[https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53402476 Azerbaijan general among troops killed in Armenia border clash] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53402476 |date=20200714193556 }}, 14 July 2020, BBC News</ref>。

